idata.author: Anonymous
idata.python:
# Dabke Instrument
kick = 0
snare = 2

# Dabke Beat
for i in range(4):  # Loop for structure
    playNote(kick, beats = 1.0)     # dum
    rest(0.5)
    playNote(snare, beats = 1.0)    # tek
    rest(0.5)
    playNote(snare, beats = 1.0)    # tek
    rest(1.0)
    playNote(kick, beats = 1.0)     # dum
    rest(0.5)
    playNote(snare, beats = 1.0)    # tek
    rest(0.5)
    playNote(snare, beats = 1.0)    # tek
    rest(1.0)
